'''飓风诺拉'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Nora}}）是[[2003年太平洋飓风季|2003年太平洋飓风季]]最后一个[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]墨西哥的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是该季第十四个获命名的风暴和第五场飓风，于10月1日经[[东风波|东风波]]发展而成。气旋朝西北方向移动并缓慢增强，于10月4日达到飓风强度。风暴在当天达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时160公里的最高强度，但由于东侧有规模更大的[[2003年飓风奥拉夫|飓风奥拉夫]]存在，诺拉无法进一步强化。受逐渐逼近的[[低压槽|低压槽]]影响，气旋在迅速减弱的同时转朝东面的墨西哥前进，到10月7日已降级成热带低气压。虽然诺拉已不再属于热带气旋，但由于其位置靠近陆地，因此[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]还在继续针对气旋发布公告。

出乎气象机构意料，诺拉重新发展出雷暴区，并于10月9日从[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]][[马萨特兰|马萨特兰]]附近登陆，之后不久就逐渐消散。低气压在墨西哥西部产生局部暴雨，但没有报导表明当地因此受到破坏，也没有出现人员伤亡。风暴残留之后同奥拉夫和[[冷心低压|下层低气压区]]融合，在德克萨斯州中部引发洪灾，还催生出一场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Nora 2003 track.png}}
9月13日，有[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸向西移动，行经[[大西洋|大西洋]]和[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]期间没有显著发展。9月25日，东风波轴线穿越[[中美洲|中美洲]]，其[[对流|对流]]沿[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]南部海岸继续西进。<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2003-11-04 | title = Hurricane Nora Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055518/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP142003_Nora.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-05-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP142003_Nora.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>9月29日，天气系统行进至[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]以南约160公里海域，其组织结构已有改善<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | date = 2003-09-29 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | accessdate = 2016-08-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193532/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2003/TWOEP.200309291019 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2003/TWOEP.200309291019 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。虽然上层[[风切变|风切变]]的不利影响尚不强烈，但[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]还是在9月30日首度指出系统有可能会在接下来数天内发展成[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | date = 2003-09-30 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | accessdate = 2016-08-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231917/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2003/TWOEP.200309301006 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2003/TWOEP.200309301006 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center }}</ref>。10月1日，雷暴已有充分组织，气象机构因此把位于[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]最南端以南约975公里洋面的天气系统归类成第十四{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压<ref name="tcr" /><ref name="d1">{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | date = 2003-10-01 | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen-E Discussion One | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303180322/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。

低气压发展期间拥有层次分明的[[大气环流|下层环流]]，并在北侧的[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响下朝正西以南方向前进。外界环境有利于进一步发展，[[风切变|风切变]]较少，[[海面温度|水温]]偏高<ref name="d1" />，促使对流逐渐组织，于10月2日清晨升级成热带风暴并获名“诺拉”（{{lang|en|Nora}}）<ref name="tcr" />。到达距高压脊最远的位置后，风暴几乎短暂停止移动<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Roberts | author2 = Avila | date = 2003-10-03 | title = Tropical Storm Nora Discussion Seven | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-26 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171655/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.007.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.007.shtml? }}</ref>，但到10月3日又开始稳步朝西北方向前进。深层对流中心发展出[[风眼|眼状特征]]<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Knabb | author2 = Franklin | date = 2003-10-03 | title = Tropical Storm Nora Discussion Nine | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313143651/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.009.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.009.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-13 }}</ref>，诺拉于10月4日清晨成为飓风，接下来还在继续增强，于当天达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]160公里的最高强度<ref name="tcr" />。气象部门此时预计，由于外界环境仍然有利，飓风的风速会继续提升至每小时185公里，达到大型飓风标准<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Knabb | author2 = Stewart | date = 2003-10-04 | title = Hurricane Nora Discussion Twelve | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313234320/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.012.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.012.shtml? | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-26 | archivedate = 2016-03-13 }}</ref>。但由于东面正在发展的[[2003年飓风奥拉夫|热带风暴奥拉夫]]导致风切变增多，诺拉实际上未能继续增强<ref name="tcr" />。

10月5日时，诺拉的风眼在卫星图像上已经无法辨别，表明飓风已开始减弱。不过，[[特殊微波传感器/成像仪|特殊微波传感器/成像仪]]的观测结果又显示气旋西北象限内形成另一个很小的风眼。<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Brown | author2 = Jarvinen | date = 2003-10-05 | title = Hurricane Nora Discussion Fifteen | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2011-06-26 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.015.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312224715/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.015.shtml }}</ref>对流渐趋混乱<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | date = 2003-10-05 | title = Hurricane Nora Discussion Seventeen | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-26 | archivedate = 2016-03-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313014132/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.017.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.017.shtml? }}</ref>，风速于10月6日降至低于飓风标准。与此同时，逐渐逼近的强烈中层[[低压槽|低压槽]]促使诺拉的移动速度减缓并转向东进<ref name="tcr" />。持续存在的风切变和干燥空气将中心附近的雷暴剥离<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2003-10-06 | title = Tropical Storm Nora Discussion Twenty-One | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160318215555/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.021.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.021.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-18 }}</ref>，到10月7日时，所有深层对流均已消亡<ref>{{cite report | author = Brian Jarvinen | date = 2003-10-07 | title = Tropical Storm Nora Discussion Twenty-Two | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-26 | archivedate = 2016-03-24 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.022.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324091234/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.022.shtml }}</ref>，风暴随即降级成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />，诺拉的强度已经降至热带气旋下限<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Brown | author2 = Pasch | date = 2003-10-07 | title = Tropical Depression Nora Discussion Twenty-Three | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | archivedate = 2016-03-21 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-08-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160321231151/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.023.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.023.shtml? }}</ref>。由于环流位置靠近墨西哥西部，同时气旋行经洋面水温较高，不能完全排除重新发展的可能，因此美国国家飓风中心继续发布公告。受逼近的低压槽影响，诺拉加速朝[[罗盘方位|东北偏东]]方向移动，之后又转向北上。<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Knab | author2 = Lawrence | date = 2003-10-08 | title = Tropical Depression Nora Discussion Twenty-Six | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160318081356/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.026.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2011-06-26 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.026.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-18 }}</ref>逼近墨西哥西部的同时，气旋中心上空又出乎气象机构意料地发展出弧形对流区<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2003-10-08 | title = Tropical Depression Nora Discussion Twenty-Nine | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-26 | archivedate = 2016-03-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160326054011/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.029.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep142003.discus.029.shtml? }}</ref>。诺拉不久就于10月9日清晨从[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]][[马萨特兰|马萨特兰]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，气旋此时尚未经过进一步发展，环流依然杂乱无章，不久后就在墨西哥西部的高山地形上空消散<ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Olaf-Nora2003filledrainblk.gif|thumb]]的降水分布，两场飓风在数天内相继吹袭墨西哥]]

美国国家飓风中心起初预测诺拉上岸时只有热带低气压强度，所以没有发布任何[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告或观察预警]]<ref name="tcr" />。不过，墨西哥国家气象局共针对风暴发布46份公告和16份预警公告。气旋在沿墨西哥海岸平行移动期间产生大浪，之后登陆锡那罗亚州时又在局部地区降下暴雨。10月8日，马萨特兰测得的24小时降雨量达到95.3毫米，比其他地点都高。10月7日降雨量最高的地方是[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]加维奥塔斯（{{lang|en|Gaviotas}}），达到87毫米。<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Servicio Meteorológico Nacional (Mexico) | date = 2003-11-26 | title = Huracán "Nora" del Océano Pacífico | accessdate = 2016-03-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165725/http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2003/pacifico/nora/nora.html | url = http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2003/pacifico/nora/nora.html }}</ref>诺拉还在[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]沿海地区产生降水，降雨范围还向北延伸到[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]附近<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090623/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/noraolaf2003.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/noraolaf2003.html | date = 2007-01-25 | title = Hurricanes Nora/Olaf - October 3–8, 2003 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | author = David M. Roth | accessdate = 2016-08-28 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。风暴对墨西哥西部的整体影响很小，没有任何报导表明当地因此遭受任何损失或有任何人员伤亡<ref name="tcr" />。

飓风诺拉和奥拉夫的残留湿气同上层低气压区相互影响，令德克萨斯州普降暴雨，[[韦科_(德克萨斯州)|韦科]]附近发生洪灾，[[麦格雷戈_(德克萨斯州)|麦格雷戈]]（{{lang|en|McGregor}}）附近一户人家被迫撤离。受洪灾影响，[[35号州际公路德克萨斯州段|35号州际公路]]、[[84号美国国道|84号国道]]和[[德克萨斯州36号州道|36号州道]]部分路段封闭。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Beaumont Enterprise | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | date = 2003-10-09 | title = Possible tornado hits Houston suburb; floods hit Waco area | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160610144649/http://www.beaumontenterprise.com/default/article/Possible-tornado-hits-Houston-suburb-floods-hit-761124.php | archivedate = 2016-06-10 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | url = http://www.beaumontenterprise.com/default/article/Possible-tornado-hits-Houston-suburb-floods-hit-761124.php }}</ref>此外，天气系统还在[[舒格兰_(得克萨斯州)|舒格兰]]催生出一场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，致使四幢楼房受到破坏，其中还包括一所学校<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Reading Eagle | date = 2003-10-11 | title = Tornadoes Hit Part of Texas | agency = Associated Press | accessdate = 2016-08-24 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=V1sxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=EqMFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3575,5864549&dq=tropical+nora&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160701064852/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=V1sxAAAAIBAJ&sjid=EqMFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3575,5864549&dq=tropical+nora&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

诺拉是[[2003年太平洋飓风季|2003年太平洋飓风季]]最后一场吹袭墨西哥的风暴，另外四场分别是[[2003年飓风伊格纳西奥|飓风伊格纳西奥]]和[[2003年飓风马蒂|马蒂]]，以及[[2003年热带风暴卡洛斯|热带风暴卡洛斯]]和奥拉夫<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center Staff | date = 2003-12-01 | title = Monthly Tropical Weather Summary | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | accessdate = 2016-08-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313014614/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/tws/MIATWSEP_nov.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/tws/MIATWSEP_nov.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-13 | work = National Hurricane Center | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] }}</ref>。

